Title: Amazing Spider-Man #16
Summary: Humted starts here (sort of)! I’ve been looking forward to this story arc and was...
body:
Title: Amazing Spider-Man #16

Summary: Humted starts here (sort of)! I’ve been looking forward to this story arc and was pleasantly surprised at the twists and turns involved in Kravens part of the story. It was inevitable that the the Connors family drama was going to tie into this arc, but I feel like it could have been a very good story on its own. I’m also optimistic that whatever bug/virus Peter has is something more interesting than a plot device used to put him at a disadvantage.

Rating: 8/10

summary: Peter: I miss Mary Jane, my wife of 3 years (minimum) and friend of 7-10 years (depending on how old the writer wants me to be...
body:
Peter: I miss Mary Jane, my wife of 3 years (minimum) and friend of 7-10 years (depending on how old the writer wants me to be atm), and I’m not ready to try to date, yet.

Everyone: Peter, she dies 6 months ago, that’s more than enough time to get over the love of your life with someone you’ve never met.
